# Vercel plugin (Cursor)

This repo deploys to **Vercel** (`apps/web`, `apps/api`, `apps/gong-mcp`). Prefer the **Vercel ecosystem plugin** over improvising CLI flags or outdated platform knowledge.

## Install (once per machine / Cursor setup)

Run from any terminal (adds plugin + skills for Cursor):

```bash
npx plugins add vercel/vercel-plugin
```

Docs: [Vercel plugin for AI coding agents](https://vercel.com/docs/agent-resources/vercel-plugin)

## Agent behavior

- For **deploy**, **preview URLs**, **`vercel env`**, **logs**, **project link**, or **Vercel-specific errors**, use the **Vercel plugin / bundled skills** and official docs rather than guessing.
- Repo-specific steps stay in **`docs/deploy-vercel.md`**; combine with plugin workflows when the user is deploying or debugging Vercel.
